SELECT
    paymentType
    ,count(*) as num
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'https://datalakeytaletu.dfs.core.windows.net/yellowtaxi/nyc/csv/puYear=2010/puMonth=01/**',
        FORMAT = 'CSV',
        HEADER_ROW = TRUE,
        FIELDTERMINATOR = '|',
        FIELDQUOTE = '"',
        PARSER_VERSION = '2.0'
    ) AS [result]
GROUP BY paymentType
ORDER BY num DESC;
